WEBVTT

00:04:58.151 --> 00:05:03.287
This village, which was known
as the ghost village up until June 1, 2017,

00:05:03.311 --> 00:05:05.911
by June 30, 2017,
had acquired such an identity

00:05:05.951 --> 00:05:09.269
that now even when the sky bows 
down to see, it knows its name.

00:05:09.269 --> 00:05:12.379
(Applause)

00:05:12.471 --> 00:05:15.761
"The water and youth of the mountains
is of no use to them.

00:05:15.761 --> 00:05:18.047
The homes, which don't
have the wisdom of old age,

00:05:18.047 --> 00:05:20.481
the spirit of youth
and the mirth of kids,

00:05:20.481 --> 00:05:22.628
those homes remain incomplete."

00:05:22.671 --> 00:05:26.087
The villagers shared many such
life lessons with us.

00:05:26.111 --> 00:05:31.711
Believe me, since seventeen years of age,
teaching people twice my age